description.2: Upon taking possession of the Soul Sword, Kitty Pryde becomes shockingly violent and wild!
description.3: The Incredible Hulk is dead! But even that won't stop him, as he begins a long and hard battle through the realm of Hel to return to the land of the living!
description.4: Iron Man vs. War Machine! 'Nuff said!
description.6: Beaten and bruised, Punisher, and his new partner Dragunov, try to settle the score with the Russian drug lords!
description.8: Back in Wundagore, frenemies Thor and Blitziana have it out with one another before Thor heads back to Earth. In Asgard, Red Norvell fights off Trolls and spends extra time with Lady Sif.
description.10: A Human Torch solo special! Blazing his own trail after leaving the FF, Johnny Storm goes on a journey to reconnect with old friends...and gets ambushed by new enemies! Can help from the savage She-Hulk save the Torch from Raptor the Renegade?
description.11: PHALANX COVENANT epilogue! In the wake of the Phalanx assault, the X-Men regroup and try to move past their ordeal. Who will stay with the X-Men, and who will leave?
description.12: Gambit guest-stars! The Ragin' Cajun and Logan head to Madripoor for a surprise party- but just find an unwelcome surprise! Former Weapon X project Maverick has returned...and is demanding a warrior's death at the hands of Wolverine!
description.16: Crystal and Quicksilver travel to Wundagore Mountain to visit Pietro's childhood nanny, Bova. When the couple arrives, they find Bova on her death bed, and her husband Fydor out of options. Will the High Evolutionary be able to save the woman who raised Pietro? And will Crystal and Quicksilver be able to escape from the "New Men" of Wundagore?
description.20: Princess Leia finds herself kidnapped by a group of rogues more rebellious than the Rebels! Luke must play his cards right when it comes to meeting a government contact for the Rebel Alliance. Is this the opportunity the Rebels have been waiting for?
description.28: It all comes down to this! The Infinity Watch is deafeated! Adam Warlock stands alone against the power of Count Abyss!
description.30: Ulic and Cay Qel-Droma are two young Jedi during a time of a Sith resurgence.
description.31: Force Works is a long way from home helping to quell a Slorenian civil war, but the problems really being to flare up when the powerful and savage creature known as Ember joins the fray!
description.32: MLF and 3-Peace go head-to-head against The People's Protection Agency and China Force, China's band of heroes! What will happen when Moonstar gets caught in the crosshares of Rabbit and Reignfire?
description.35: A who's who of Marvel anti-heroes join the Secret Defenders in their fight to stop the new menace, Slaymaker!
description.38: While Douglock, Cannonball and Wolfsbane have been captured and are about to be built into the Phalanx beacon, Forge is under the mind control of the Phalanx! Can the team break free of their physical and mental constraints?
description.39: The search for Agamemnon continues! Hulk and his friends forge an alliance with old friends in Asgard. They're certainly going to need the extra help, considering they're headed to battle the Frost Giants of Jotunheim!
description.40: While Iron Man and War Machine go toe-to-toe, the Mandarin prepares to end his time spent in isolation.
description.42: The Punisher gets knocked out by Russian drug lords!
description.43: Odin explains the truth behind the Don Blake situation, and Thor must come to terms with his father's decisions.
description.45: Fantastic Four no more! After the stunning events of the battle with the Dark Raider, the team can't handle the tension...and disbands! The story retold by a man that bore witness to it all...Scott Lang, Ant-Man! Plus, a solo adventure for the ever-lovin' blue-eyed Thing!
description.46: PHALANX COVENANT tie-in! Paige Guthrie has been captured along with several other young mutants. Can they escape the grasp of the Phalanx?
description.48: PHALANX COVENANT tie-in! The epic conclusion to the GENERATION NEXT! Witness the final confrontation between Harvest and the mutant heroes.  Who will make the ultimate sacrifice?
description.51: The team is overjoyed when the spirit of Professor X is in the body of the new "Prosh"! Unfortunately, there are a few catches.
description.53: The Hulk gets possessed by a rare magic—courtesy of Vincent Stevens!
description.55: In a flashback, M.O.D.O.K. discovers the existence of a being greater than he...
description.57: Galen Kor is revealed to be behind Mephistoid's reincarnation. Deathcry becomes disheartened when she discovers Alabar doesn't live up to his legendary reputation. Witness the fall of Deathcry!
description.59: Psionex returns with a vengeance against the New Warriors!
description.61: In the conclusion to the adventures of'R2-D2'and'C-3PO'in the'Kalarba system, a power core rupture on'Hosk'forces all life forms to be evacuated, but life forms doesn't include'droids! As'Olag Greck'makes his final stand, R2-D2 and C-3PO race against time to save the industrial'moon, but first they'll have to survive Greck's droid armada!
description.62: Featuring classic adventures from the early age of Star Wars! In the first issue, C3PO and R2-D2 must locate a missing Luke and Leia on an anti-droid planet!
description.63: The Watch confronts Count Abyss face to face at last! Can the team defeat him and still manage to save Maya from his clutches?
description.69: It's up to a small Jedi task force to stop a Sith-fueled uprising.
description.70: Force Works' baptism of fire isn't over yet! The new team has their hands full when taking on a mysterious alien race known only as the Scatter!
description.73: The Secret Defenders vs. Swarm! Even with their new teammates, they'll need help from Iceman and Angel of the X-Men!
description.75: Daredevil vs. Hydra! Can the Man Without Fear stop Baron von Strucker from drowning New York City in his evil? And will he be able to do it in time to save Captain America?
description.77: Hulk and the Pantheon begin their search for their mysterious friend Agamemnon! First stop: the realm eternal, Asgard!
description.78: Iron Man and Vor/Tex clash while the Mandarin searches for his rings of power.
description.80: Two Russians attempting to push heroin into New York receive a calling card from the Punisher.
description.82: The only way to find out the truth about Don Blake is for Thor to...fight Thor? That's right- Odin has created another son, and the two must now compete in battle!
description.84: X-Factor, Excalibur, and X-Force all face up in battle against the terror of the Phalanx! Can the three teams combined take down their techno-organic enemy? Don’t bet on it.
description.85: The identity of the Dark Raider, the villain planning to murder every Reed Richards in the multiverse, is revealed! How can you stop the murderous rampage of a man out for revenge...against himself?
description.86: PHALANX COVENANT tie-in! The X-Mansion is under attack! With almost the entire team under the control of the Phalanx, Banshee must turn to the unlikeliest of allies.
description.87: A PHALANX COVENENT tie-in! Wolverine drops in to help Cyclops and Jean take on the Phalanx, but he may have bitten off more than he can chew this time! Plus - Cable makes startling discoveries about his past!
description.88: PHALANX COVENANT tie-in! The forces of the Phalanx are hunting down the next generation of mutant heroes! Can the X-Men save them before they're assimilated?
description.91: A Battle Royale with Shriek and Carrion! Spider-Man has his hands full taking down two of the most unstable villains he's ever faced. You won't want to miss the shocking conclusion to this issue!
description.92: Avengers Magdalene, Swordsman, Vision, and Deathcry, arrive in Scotland to check on a remote tracking station. While there, the Avengers encounter a disgraced Shi'ar warrior, and fall under the influence of the Mephisitoid! Who is the Mephisitoid? And will the team be able to escape its mind-altering powers?
description.93: The team roster is larger than ever as the “New” Warriors take center stage!
description.96: Forge reveals that a major techno-organic Phalanx embryo is about to erupt.
description.99: Enter—Polaris! The X-Factor powerhouse may find herself merged with Doctor Strange after Stevens rejects the offer.

1.text: Ed and Ralph are falsely accused and arrested for bombing buildings.  As Daredevil attempts at clearing their names, he runs into trouble.

7.text: Ben Reilly throws down with Venom and a symbiote spawn!

9.text: Until recently, Mystique was presumed dead. But Forge has picked up the shapeshifter's trail and along with his teammates, he follows it to Israel to uncover the truth.

13.text: After conducting extensive research on the Legacy Virus, Beast draws some grim conclusions…

21.text: SINS OF THE PAST PART 3 What does Black Tom want with Deadpool's healing factor? Can the Merc catch a break?

22.text: Spidey struggles to break free from his restraints in Ravencroft, while Ben Reilly heads to the rescue!

23.text: PAYBACK! Kasey Nash, Gabriel's wild and rebellious sister, has been kidnapped by Stark-Fujikawa and transformed into a living weapon!

24.text: Peter Parker encounters an identical stranger on the rooftops of Manhattan. In his anger and confusion he gives chase to hunt this doppelganger down!

25.text: The mysterious clone of Spider-Man ruminates on the path he has followed the last several years of his life just before a strange visitor presents him with an offer he may not be able to refuse.

26.text: The X-Men vs. the Phalanx! Along with Cyclops, Jean Grey, and Wolverine, Cable stages an all-out assault on the Phalanx citadel! Can they take it down, or is all of mutantkind doomed to assimilation?

27.text: Cap's condition has taken a turn for the worse, and the wicked Baron Zemo wants to finish Cap for good!

28.text: It all comes down to this! The Infinity Watch is deafeated! Adam Warlock stands alone against the power of Count Abyss!

31.text: Force Works is a long way from home helping to quell a Slorenian civil war, but the problems really being to flare up when the powerful and savage creature known as Ember joins the fray!

32.text: MLF and 3-Peace go head-to-head against The People's Protection Agency and China Force, China's band of heroes! What will happen when Moonstar gets caught in the crosshares of Rabbit and Reignfire?

33.text: It's the Guardians' final battle against Korvac and his Intimidators!

34.text: Spider-Man and Ghost Rider, they ain't! Venom and Vengeance carve a swath of carnage through the Stalkers, but when they're face to face with the group's leader, they may find they've gotten into more than they've bargained for!

35.text: A who's who of Marvel anti-heroes join the Secret Defenders in their fight to stop the new menace, Slaymaker!

36.text: THE BATTLE OF THE CENTURY! Drax the Destroyer goes against The Irish Wolfhound!

37.text: Daredevil saves a homeless man from being attacked and is led through sewer tunnels where he must battle The King.

38.text: While Douglock, Cannonball and Wolfsbane have been captured and are about to be built into the Phalanx beacon, Forge is under the mind control of the Phalanx! Can the team break free of their physical and mental constraints?

44.text: STRONG GUY versus BLOB in an absolute punch-a-rama!

47.text: Temporal hiccups have Wolverine's past, present and future under distress.

49.text: Peter Parker and his clone Ben Reilly join forces in an effort to defeat the Traveler!

51.text: The team is overjoyed when the spirit of Professor X is in the body of the new "Prosh"! Unfortunately, there are a few catches.

53.text: The Hulk gets possessed by a rare magic—courtesy of Vincent Stevens!

58.text: When Scorpio, who's in possession of the Cosmic Key, falls to Hydra, it will be up to Wolverine and Nick Fury to get him back.

60.text: Hawkeye joins the fray! Will the ace archer tip the scales in defeating Arul and Deathtoll? Plus, Clint eases James’ guilt over taking lives.

63.text: The Watch confronts Count Abyss face to face at last! Can the team defeat him and still manage to save Maya from his clutches?

64.text: SINS OF THE PAST PART 2 Siryn must take Deadpool to a safe place until he can heal. But Black Tom has sent Juggernaut looking for the Merc With A Mouth and he won't exactly be waiting for Wilson to catch his breath!

65.text: Gabriel knows the truth about Miguel's secret identity. Miguel must seek help from an old flame.

66.text: He's clashed with Stryfe, he's tangled with Omega Red, and he's survived some of the most hellish battles you can possibly imagine. But is Cable ready for the ultimate challenge…a date with Domino?

67.text: Is this the next Sentinel of Liberty? Introducing Free Spirit!

70.text: Force Works' baptism of fire isn't over yet! The new team has their hands full when taking on a mysterious alien race known only as the Scatter!

71.text: The shapeshifting Replica turns on her teammates – but to what end?

72.text: Venom and Vengeance fight off the Stalkers, but a hostage situation leaves them with an ultimatum!

73.text: The Secret Defenders vs. Swarm! Even with their new teammates, they'll need help from Iceman and Angel of the X-Men!

74.text: Talon undergoes a magnificent change…AND DRAX THE DESTROYER IS BACK AND BETTER THAN EVER!

84.text: X-Factor, Excalibur, and X-Force all face up in battle against the terror of the Phalanx! Can the three teams combined take down their techno-organic enemy? Don’t bet on it.

94.text: Deathtoll’s past is slowly revealed, although questions still remain about his motives. Plus, James confronts questions his morality when it comes to taking lives.

95.text: The return of Net Prophet! What will future Spidey encounter from his Interspace foe in his first Annual? Three Spider-Man 2099 stories combined in one explosive issue!

96.text: Forge reveals that a major techno-organic Phalanx embryo is about to erupt.

97.text: Cyclops and Jean Grey must travel abroad…to the Savage Land!

99.text: Enter—Polaris! The X-Factor powerhouse may find herself merged with Doctor Strange after Stevens rejects the offer.
